{"tid":621141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過一見到張相，眼淚就忍唔住流出嚟","createTime":"2018-04-08T05:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:46:20.000Z","uid":72071,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b79baa4819a0e3e6216c66a12175d6d3891ee6d","tid":621141,"uid":72071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且就係今日<br />\n<br />\n今早我係台灣機場返黎香港嗰陣<br />\n進入離境大堂之前影左一張相&hellip;<br />\n其實相片好普通，只係一個柔弱女生站著，望過黎既一刻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢係我女朋友&hellip;<br />\n明明今次黎台灣見佢每日都開心到不得了<br />\n至昨晚我既情緒都冇咁波動，但到我睇返張相，我好唔舍得<br />\n亦都係咁問自己，點解可以俾一個女仔去咁樣睇住我離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想好想快啲賺錢將佢娶過黎&hellip; <br />\n唔想再同佢分開&hellip;<br />\n好掛住佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲打見到一個人今朝坐緊地火車眼濕濕，嗰個可能係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694d2f3ab8379bd10736eb8d948a8b3aadb43a14","tid":621141,"uid":23468,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">巴打條女係台妹？你一走佢轉頭就抽插緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"d4de75785bcdede28fd00666eb54011778f4640b","tid":621141,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"自拍照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c855acbb74e69ba14e9089790ea62276de8ab5","tid":621141,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfd0e5ac3305e836de4a0b27b50417902ae30602","tid":621141,"uid":19312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-0